author: Jeffery Martin
title: Washington Enacts Stay-at-Home Order, Social Bans Include Weddings and Funerals
description: "This also applies to some of the most important gatherings in people's lives, like weddings and funerals," Inslee said Monday. "For the sake of all, even these occasions have to be postponed."
content: Washington Governor Jay Inslee announced a stay-at-home order for a minimum of two weeks for Washington state Monday during a televised address. Inslee said the order would go into effect Wednesday and ban many social gatherings, including weddings and funera… [+2753 chars]
